Sentece: In more than 600 patient-treatments, bone marrow toxicity was negligible (mean absolute neutrophil count [ANC] > 2.0 x 10(9)/L).
Title: Results of a clinical trial in humans with refractory cancer of the intracellular histamine antagonist, N,N-diethyl-2-[4-(phenylmethyl)phenoxy]ethanamine-HCl, in combination with various single antineoplastic agents.
Name: Tesmilifene
